1
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,599
Mystic Water Hall

2
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:04,280
So this is what Uncle Ye spoke of,

3
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,480
the place where I can find my origins.

4
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:17,919
Medicine's Fate Returns to Origin.

5
00:02:17,919 --> 00:02:19,159
Mystic Water, break the seal.

6
00:02:19,159 --> 00:02:19,879
Cloud Qi, return to the vessel.

7
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:20,960
Soul Seal, reveal thyself.

8
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:07,919
It's you.

9
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:12,199
An incident occurred at the Medicine King Ceremony,

10
00:04:12,199 --> 00:04:13,960
and Green Wood Hall faced sudden upheaval.

11
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,400
For the sake of the greater good,

12
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:18,639
several Association Stewards have decided

13
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:19,959
to merge the Herb Mastery Examination

14
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:22,160
with the first round of the Healer's Path.

15
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:23,920
Look, Ye Qingxue is here,

16
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,519
and why is that fake Yang Family orphan here?

17
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,519
If I remember correctly,

18
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:47,040
anyone unverified by the Mystic Medicine

19
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,560
Association can't join the Healer's Path.

20
00:04:50,319 --> 00:04:51,120
Sorry to disappoint,

21
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:54,240
but this time I did bring proof.

22
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:03,399
Let's see what proof you have.

23
00:05:09,519 --> 00:05:10,879
Yang Yunfan.

24
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:14,240
Father: Yang Mingyuan.

25
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:15,560
What does this mean?

26
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,720
It's a birth certificate.

27
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,319
He really is Yang Yunfan?

28
00:05:19,319 --> 00:05:19,800
Who is it?

29
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,959
You don't seriously think a single paper

30
00:05:26,959 --> 00:05:29,560
proves you're the Yang Family orphan?

31
00:05:31,199 --> 00:05:32,240
That's hardly convincing.

32
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,079
Not convincing at all.

33
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:45,519
I can vouch for it.

34
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,560
It's you.

35
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,720
The paper may be old,

36
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:20,000
but its Mystic Water Hall seal is real.

37
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:22,920
I sealed this birth certificate myself.

38
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,240
Song Ci

39
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,639
It wouldn't be hard to forge, right?

40
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:48,800
Lady Song

41
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,519
Wait.

42
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:50,000
Lady Song, what are you doing?

43
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:50,639
Come here

44
00:06:52,199 --> 00:06:53,399
Do you still want to compete?

45
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:54,360
Lady Song, I'm begging you

46
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:54,680
Leave me some dignity

47
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,600
I've already seen it all

48
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:02,040
The birth certificate states

49
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:04,639
he has a unique birthmark on his lower back

50
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,319
Birth certificates can be faked

51
00:07:07,319 --> 00:07:08,800
but birthmarks cannot

52
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:10,800
It's really there

53
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,879
Let me see if it's real

54
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,959
It really is there

55
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:14,959
Look, he really has it

56
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,360
Stop looking

57
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,199
It seems to be real

58
00:07:24,279 --> 00:07:25,040
Alright

59
00:07:31,759 --> 00:07:33,439
Yang Yunfan's identity is verified

60
00:07:33,439 --> 00:07:34,160
He is permitted to compete

61
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:47,040
Medicine Master Li is letting him compete?

62
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:49,040
Why didn't you tell me before?

63
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,560
Whether my identity as Yang heir is real,

64
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:58,279
I'll always be the fiancé by your side.

65
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:00,759
Qingxue

66
00:08:02,879 --> 00:08:03,959
This time, you must trust me

67
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,600
I will definitely win

68
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:08,040
I'll make those people pay

69
00:08:09,879 --> 00:08:10,519
Alright

70
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:19,680
The prescriptions you hold are the test

71
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,040
Please examine them carefully

72
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,759
Contestants, listen carefully

73
00:08:27,759 --> 00:08:30,240
Before me lies the Misty Herb Sanctuary

74
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,319
Today's examination

75
00:08:31,319 --> 00:08:33,639
is a dual trial of character and skill

76
00:08:33,639 --> 00:08:36,039
Contestants, within two hours

77
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:38,039
you must reach Violet Herb Garden on foot

78
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,960
No external aid is permitted

79
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:42,840
Rely only on stamina, skill, and judgment

80
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:45,120
I hope each of you can forge your own path

81
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:48,440
The Association is going all out this year

82
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,600
Even opening the Misty Herb Sanctuary

83
00:08:50,279 --> 00:08:51,000
Indeed

84
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,919
I heard that this place

85
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:54,759
even a Medicine Master couldn't enter.

86
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:56,919
What Misty Herb Sanctuary?

87
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:57,759
Sounds pretty intimidating

88
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,399
Is it worth getting so excited over?

89
00:09:02,799 --> 00:09:05,639
It's the core of the Association's herbs.

90
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:08,879
Many rare herbs are grown here

91
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:10,879
It's also a forbidden ground where past

92
00:09:10,879 --> 00:09:12,840
Medicine Venerables inherited the Primordial Violet Qi Art.

93
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:14,480
Forbidden ground?

94
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,120
How thrilling

95
00:09:17,159 --> 00:09:18,759
Is that the point?

96
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:21,120
Then what is?

97
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:23,879
The point is the Primordial Violet Qi Art

98
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:26,039
They say the Primordial Violet Qi Art

99
00:09:26,039 --> 00:09:29,279
is an art born of spiritual essence.

100
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:31,000
It can cure any ailment

101
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,919
Sadly, spiritual essence has dwindled

102
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:34,840
and it's extremely difficult to practice.

103
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,279
Aside from the Medicine Venerable

104
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:38,200
almost no one knows its true formula

105
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:45,600
You

106
00:09:47,039 --> 00:09:48,840
Hand over the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art, now!

107
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,240
The Master has issued a kill order on you

108
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,919
I just know he's tied to the Mystic Medicine Association.

109
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:05,960
Alright.

110
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:07,799
Does anyone have any questions

111
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:09,320
regarding the rules?

112
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:12,039
Um, Deputy Herb Overseer Song,

113
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:13,519
this prescription...

114
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:15,120
how do we navigate without any roads?

115
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:16,519
Weren't there supposed to be hints?

116
00:10:16,519 --> 00:10:18,519
I thought this was a map.

117
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:20,039
The clues to the destination

118
00:10:20,039 --> 00:10:22,320
are hidden in the prescriptions you hold.

119
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:24,519
You must figure it out yourselves.

120
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:30,440
Alright.

121
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:32,799
The competition now officially begins.

122
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:40,879
Let's go!

123
00:10:40,879 --> 00:10:41,600
We'll head out first.

124
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,200
Go!

125
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:42,960
Hurry!

126
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:43,799
Xiang, my son.

127
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,120
Father.

128
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,759
Remember,

129
00:10:54,759 --> 00:10:56,399
the competition matters,

130
00:10:56,399 --> 00:10:57,960
but don't only think about winning.

131
00:10:59,159 --> 00:11:00,120
The Healer's Path

132
00:11:00,799 --> 00:11:02,639
lies in observation.

133
00:11:02,639 --> 00:11:03,399
I know what I'm doing.

134
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:05,759
Good.

135
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,240
Go on then.

136
00:11:07,919 --> 00:11:09,600
Good son-in-law, you can do it!

137
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,200
Good luck!

138
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:22,120
Know your place.

139
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:25,639
Don't forget how your father survived.

140
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,440
Go now.

141
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,320
Move it!

142
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:35,240
Hurry!

143
00:11:35,759 --> 00:11:36,559
Aren't we going?

144
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:38,480
Hold on.

145
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:38,840
No rush.

146
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:40,720
Look closely at this prescription again.

147
00:11:41,519 --> 00:11:42,879
The herbs listed here,

148
00:11:42,879 --> 00:11:44,600
Dragon Whisker Grass, Prince Ginseng,

149
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:45,759
goji berries, and White Atractylodes,

150
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:48,960
they each have unique growing conditions

151
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,080
and geographic locations.

152
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,440
You mean,

153
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:54,559
these herbs will guide us forward?

154
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,120
Exactly.

155
00:11:56,639 --> 00:11:58,399
Herbs that thrive in cold, damp shade

156
00:11:58,399 --> 00:11:59,759
mostly grow in valleys.

157
00:11:59,759 --> 00:12:02,679
While sun-loving herbs grow on hillsides.

158
00:12:02,679 --> 00:12:05,159
Our destination, Violet Herb Garden, is sunny.

159
00:12:05,159 --> 00:12:08,120
These herbs may seem listed at random,

160
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,240
but they're actually arranged

161
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,960
by their geographic locations.

162
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,000
This way,

163
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,360
finding Violet Herb Garden becomes easy.

164
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,399
Let's go.

165
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:18,480
Okay.

166
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,600
Just let him go.

167
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,679
No one can stop him.

168
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:41,320
Misty Herb Sanctuary is quite beautiful.

169
00:12:53,799 --> 00:12:54,720
Something's off.

170
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,159
What is it?

171
00:12:57,639 --> 00:12:59,559
The herbal scent here is heavy and stuffy.

172
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,639
It's a bit strange,

173
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:05,000
it doesn't seem natural.

174
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:07,960
You're overthinking it.

175
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,799
This is the Misty Herb Sanctuary.

176
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:12,000
Of course the herbal scent is strong.

177
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,559
Young master,

178
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:15,519
clearly it's your first time competing.

179
00:13:16,519 --> 00:13:17,519
You're too nervous,

180
00:13:17,519 --> 00:13:18,759
you're even hallucinating.

181
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,000
What's happening?

182
00:13:27,679 --> 00:13:29,120
It's poisonous miasma!

183
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,480
Hold your breath! Don't breathe it in!

184
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:56,480
Such a petty trick.

185
00:13:57,399 --> 00:14:00,039
A mere miasma dares to block my way?

186
00:14:14,039 --> 00:14:15,120
This is the last vial.

187
00:14:38,399 --> 00:14:39,039
I can't

188
00:14:39,039 --> 00:14:39,840
I can't breathe

189
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:41,120
This miasma is toxic

190
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:42,559
My throat's burning like fire

191
00:14:42,559 --> 00:14:43,399
Retreat, now!

192
00:14:48,279 --> 00:14:49,480
Let's go!

193
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,759
Staying here means death

194
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:57,320
Qingxue, look at me

195
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,759
The violet qi forms a barrier

196
00:15:02,759 --> 00:15:04,320
to ward off evil spirits,

197
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:06,080
making us immune to all poisons.

198
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,039
Much better

199
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,240
See? I told you

200
00:15:11,240 --> 00:15:12,519
Carrying two of you is no problem.

201
00:15:12,519 --> 00:15:13,440
Flying with you is a piece of cake.

202
00:15:14,799 --> 00:15:15,960
We should get going

203
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,519
It's too dangerous

204
00:15:18,679 --> 00:15:20,120
Help me

205
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:23,600
Save me

206
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,639
Hang in there.

207
00:15:41,559 --> 00:15:42,440
Feeling any better?

208
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,720
Thanks for saving my life, brother.

209
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,639
But the competition must go on.

210
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,440
Allow me to go on ahead.

211
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,720
If you save everyone,

212
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:13,200
you won't even hold on to last place.

213
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,159
First to the summit gets a trophy.

214
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,320
Last to the summit gets friends.

215
00:16:17,759 --> 00:16:18,559
Let's go.

216
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:33,600
Save me!

217
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:34,159
Xiangyang.

218
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,320
Please save me!

219
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,919
No one can stop me

220
00:16:38,919 --> 00:16:40,320
from getting the Primordial Violet Qi Art.

221
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:47,320
Hurry, save me! Save me!

222
00:16:52,639 --> 00:16:53,840
Don't go!

223
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:54,559
Save me!

224
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:57,279
Don't go!

225
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:04,200
Save me!

226
00:17:05,799 --> 00:17:06,680
I'm begging you!

227
00:17:14,759 --> 00:17:16,799
Why is there a patient on the mountain?

228
00:17:16,799 --> 00:17:18,160
Doesn't matter who he is.

229
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:18,960
Save him first, ask later.

230
00:17:41,519 --> 00:17:42,160
Come on.

231
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:42,839
Come over to me.

232
00:17:58,720 --> 00:17:59,839
Young man

233
00:17:59,839 --> 00:18:01,240
Are you an immortal?

234
00:18:02,359 --> 00:18:03,759
Immortals might not save people,

235
00:18:03,759 --> 00:18:04,440
but I do.

236
00:18:24,599 --> 00:18:25,759
A speed race

237
00:18:25,759 --> 00:18:27,279
How did it turn into a medical patrol?

238
00:19:30,359 --> 00:19:31,319
First place:

239
00:19:31,319 --> 00:19:32,799
Li Xiangyang of Red Fire Hall

240
00:19:55,799 --> 00:19:56,920
Second place:

241
00:19:56,920 --> 00:19:59,079
Lu Tanxiang, Lu Family of Mystic Water Hall

242
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:11,799
Third place:

243
00:20:11,799 --> 00:20:13,119
Lin Yu of the Gilded Hall

244
00:20:17,839 --> 00:20:19,559
And the final spot...

245
00:20:20,599 --> 00:20:23,720
The real show's about to begin
